        <h5>Standard Lot EUR/USD Trade</h5>
        <p><strong>Pepperstone:</strong> 0.09 pip spread = $0.90 + $7 commission = $7.90 per round turn</p>
        <p><strong>IC Markets:</strong> 0.02 pip spread = $0.20 + $7 commission = $7.20 per round turn</p>
